{"tid":1943817,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"假戲、真話 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-03-26T03:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T04:59:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d883af807866200c1888a2fd3088e00bf585e66a","tid":1943817,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200325/20886662/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200325%2F20886662%2F&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Zvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=98dc0195\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200325%2F20886662%2F&h=90229188\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200325/20886662/</a><br />\n<br />\n假戲、真話 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200325/large/1585032577_596e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200325%2Flarge%2F1585032577_596e.jpg&h=3fc08cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《微博》截圖<br />\n<br />\n真是造假專業國。為了武漢肺炎疫情的暖新聞，動用了不少影視人拍了又拍，扮反映現實，題材不外維穩定民心，極煽情。不贅。<br />\n<br />\n又收到視頻，媽媽帶着女兒去醫院探望醫生爸爸，只聽得一聲「roll」，女兒字正腔圓：「爸爸，我想抱抱你！」爸爸隔着玻璃伸手難觸，又字正腔圓道：「寶貝，聽話喔！再過些時間，爸爸出去了，一定還你一個世界上最大的擁抱！」修飾造作的台詞，不是真心話，無情緒反應。<br />\n<br />\n說到真心話，很多人原本不大在意港大袁國勇和龍振邦的《大流行緣起武漢，十七年教訓盡忘》一文，是在更正、撤稿、道歉、表忠之後，才找來一看：人話、真話、專業見解，錯在哪？科學家不管政治，政治管上門，也好，「曲線廣傳」反收大效，如今人人都看過了，也更明白是非黑白了。<br />\n<br />\n大陸除了視頻廣傳欺哄百姓，還籌拍抗疫劇集《在一起》，不知欽點的陳道明是否樂意演鍾南山？目前鍾受捧，卻沒說真話的自由，奉命把病毒源頭諉過美國，若干年後還是「英雄」嗎？<br />\n<br />\n為了一睹老戲骨陳道明近貌（有點膠），看了一集《慶餘年》，說是大陸人氣劇，誤中副車留意到男主角范閑，也許他想模仿當年浪子姜大衛，一不小心，十分之鄧兆尊，笑死。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"e6336b05af19af8e258c8c7abc530cf34182a1f7","tid":1943817,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1943881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1943881</a><br />\n聯署facebook專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flegcopetition&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Zvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=b0825434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/legcopetition</a><br />\n聯署Link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/LHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FLHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA&d=8fAJgc%2Bq%2B0y88RV8Svjv4Zvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=34e65eff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/LHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dNkmvj1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdNkmvj1.png&h=43c49fd0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}